The capital city of Elenath, Flame's Crest is a large city, the largest on the continent. 
A center for arts, science, trade, and much more, it is set into a valley surrounded by the Crystal Mountains. 
A circular city with the palace at its heart, each ring is separated by a canal which are crossed by 4 bridges, one for each direction. 
The circles are not organize by economic level but rather by the focus on that area. 
The inner circle houses the royal palace along with many law buildlings. 
The next circle focuses on arts and fashion. 
Next is religion. And the final, science and medicine.
